headline: BMO Capital Keeps Moody’s (MCO) at Market Perform, Raises PT to $534
summary: Moody’s Corporation (NYSE:MCO) is one of the best long-term stocks to invest in according to Warren Buffett. On August 22, BMO Capital reiterated a “Market Perform” rating for Moody’s with a price target of $534. The decision follows leadership changes at Moody’s.
